{"tid":1499393,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我本身打算移民 經過今日 我會選擇死係香港","createTime":"2019-08-23T16:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T17:27:36.000Z","uid":112001,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"141a4fed1997413d800026bc2c2890612882d3ed","tid":1499393,"uid":112001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:41:29.000Z","msg":"先講心底說話，我到今日之前都冇諗過香港之路有用，更加冇諗過會成功連到全香港。<br />\n岩岩幾個鐘，由一開始到到都唔夠人，去到爆哂人，有啲位仲排到兩行，係我兩個月來最震撼嘅一次。我發夢上過前線，望過手足朋友被拉，食過好撚多tg，一直以來堅持我每次出來都係呢班手足。但去到今日，我見到當呢件事一步一步走向攬炒嘅時候，出來支持我地嘅人反而越來越多。學林建波講，呢個明明係佢地嘅收成期，但呢班老人家，父母，仍然無條件咁支持呢場運動，我先第一次感受到香港人係幾咁團結。望住一班伯伯婆婆企足兩個鐘，拖住班後生仔女，叫佢地小心，我終於明白點解我地一直守護嘅野係乜野。<br />\n香港人或者好自私，好功利，但絕對係呢個世界上我最愛嘅人。我知道來緊我地將會面對嘅係更恐怖嘅政權同暴力，但我希望大家明白，掌握香港人命運嘅，唔係中共，唔係美國，唔係咩外國勢力，係我地自己。<br />\n希望大家應承我，唔好絕望，唔好拋低任何一位手足，要堅持到攞返我地嘅香港。而我亦應承大家，雖然我好微小，但亦會抗爭到我生命嘅最後一刻。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"e6323794a04abb8b8171144a26be4090870879d2","tid":1499393,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:42:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fcall-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6rktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=1579e451\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手簽確認中共係恐佈份子 加速中共解體速度"},{"pid":"d16b273d239b0ffa4cdaa2ed0297f6f96fb8da72","tid":1499393,"uid":112001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:43:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日機場見</span>"},{"pid":"8fe6d505138cc7991542eb48f7a35813eef43732","tid":1499393,"uid":26405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"同感"},{"pid":"7816f6207968ab44e97b4e4152df12e3df4ce988","tid":1499393,"uid":56900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:45:51.000Z","msg":"無啦啦簽唔到"},{"pid":"10086591afd88333af8e7062a99b14cc24ed3d08","tid":1499393,"uid":118350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f607fc6d82b2033c53f69818222cf29eb64419","tid":1499393,"uid":112001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"打完飛機要推返正經野，大家聽日見"},{"pid":"a27a5035c487cf966e53649769f14a8c5ca09ec7","tid":1499393,"uid":311198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:50:54.000Z","msg":"我自己有外國護照住喺外國但因為今次運動比香港人感動返，決定唔可以放棄屋企！"},{"pid":"57985bcca85baa2b3883e0fe904d846b8f2220b3","tid":1499393,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b874b40e79dbd7035e59dc4e5dd86b17b0964b1e","tid":1499393,"uid":260934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"同感"},{"pid":"e012224433613caa242f90dbbdf59e6b1edaf862","tid":1499393,"uid":179548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:12:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87389994cd54699b5dd7f8a2df85854ae57708b4","tid":1499393,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:15:42.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n824 825<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ebe6bc9ff0889a0ebe2530d0425eef7d69f64e","tid":1499393,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d16b273d239b0ffa4cdaa2ed0297f6f96fb8da72","tid":1499393,"uid":112001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:43:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日機場見</span>"},"citedBy":0,"